4:
Lord Adjudicus... How could you
betray us like this?
6:
You know better than anyone else
what the Lord of Shadow is trying to
do... How he has suffered, and how
he strives to save our people!
15:
If you've no intention to fight, then
surrender. Our forces downstairs will
receive you without hostility.
22: Did we do it? Is that the last of them?
29:
More of these stupid machines?!
How many damn punching bags
are they gonna throw at us?
34: What the hell is this place?
38:
Look, up there. That's it. The Antipode
Lance.
51:
Lady Marly, are you all right? Can
you hear me?
57:
Hehehe! Almost had you there,
didn't I?
60:
Well, well, if it isn't the filthy traitor
Adjudicus. I can't say I'm surprised,
though.
64: That's the same guy from before!
73:
I was very careful in cutting him to
pieces last time. Clearly what he
said about daemons not dying was
true...
75:
But this changes nothing. No matter
how many times you come before
us, we will decimate you again and
again!
80:
HAHAHAHA! Yes, yes, you're super
strong, I get it.
82:
That's precisely why I've brought
some extra help this time around.
87:
You! Why the hell are you here of all
places?
99:
This one is a present I got from Lady
Stella. I have to say, he's one of my
favorites. What, did I catch you off
guard? HAHA.
104:
Aaaagh! Nimbus... You
good-for-nothing... If it wasn't for
you... None of this...
110:
Damn you! STOP! Stop this right
now! Camir!
119:
HAHAHAHA! Oh yes, perfect.
I really have to thank you, Adjudicus.
122:
I never could stand you. I despised
you, really. But now, I get to have the
pleasure of ending your miserable
life myself!
125:
And YOU are going to help me do
that, pathetic little human.
128:
You and I share the same
resentment and hatred for these
miserable fools. Let's make that
dream a reality!
137:
You... took him away from me...
Lord Rolan! GIVE HIM BACK!
